notes:
This pack is interesting the rare/uncommons are mostly cards that you'd much rather be passed because while [Bloodbond Vampire] and [Resolute Blademaster] are both pretty great in the right deck, there's no guarantee the deck is available first pick.

On the other hand both [Touch of the Void] and [Complete Disregard] are solid if unexciting first picks with the nod probably going to [Touch of the Void] for colour preference reasons.
